sentences: Arild Staffan Möller (born 26 March 1955), known professionally as Ale Möller, is a Swedish musician and composer.
He was born and grew up in Scania in southern Sweden and started in music as a jazz trumpeter.
He lived for a while in Greece where he learned to play the bouzouki and played with composer Mikis Theodorakis.
